components.name: LineChart
components.query:
SELECT DISTINCT extract(year from invoice_date)::text AS year,
AVG(sales_amount) over(partition by extract(year from invoice_date)) AS sales,
AVG(quantity) over(partition by extract(year from invoice_date)) AS quantity
FROM karamschema.sales
WHERE invoice_date

components.name: BubbleChart
components.query:
select distinct extract(year from invoice_date)::text as year,
sum(sales_amount) as sales,
count(sales_id)::integer as count,
0 as some,
avg(sales_amount / quantity) as ball_size
from karamschema.sales
group by year
order by year
components.title: Bubble

components.name: SankeyChart
components.query:
select pd.item_code, cd.name, sum(sales_amount) FROM karamschema.sales as ks
INNER JOIN karamschema.product_description as pd ON ks.item_id = pd.item_id
INNER JOIN karamschema.client_description as cd ON ks.client_id = cd.client_id
where extract(year from invoice_date) = '2018' and sales_amount > 0
group by pd.item_code, cd.name limit 10
components.title: Sankey
